<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM4.6">
<l>miṉṉaṉaiya nuṇṇiṭaiyā ruruppaciyum mēṉakaiyum</l>
<l>aṉṉavartam pāṭaloṭu māṭalavai yātariyēṉ</l>
<l>teṉṉaveṉa vaṇṭiṉaṅkaḷ paṇpāṭum vēṅkaṭattuḷ</l>
<l>ḷaṉṉaṉaiya poṟkuvaṭā maruntavatta ṉāvēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The singing and the dancing of people like</l>
<l rend="indent">Ūrvaśī and Menakā, women with lightning-like slender waists</l>
<l rend="indent">- I shall not wish for those.</l>
<l>I shall have the rare [fruit of] tapas of becoming such a golden mountain as Veṅkaṭa,</l>
<l rend="indent">in which swarms of bees hum the paṇ-melody saying ‘teṉṉa’.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
